name: GMSTNSKLLo4
description:
In the real world when I design jewelry I always avoid the skull shape as the main form or supporting element of my design. I was too scared and thought the skull was too bold and would dominate the beauty of the shape I made. The combination of colorful resin colors and clean skulls I dared to realize in the digital world. Let's just say skull is my fear and I keep it in myself as an aesthetic element in my life, enjoyy
